{
  "texts": [
    "Feature or concept removal requests.",
    "Requests for feature removal are concerned with specific attributes about data points.",
    "This is well defined for tabular data, where attributes correspond to one or more columns of the tables.",
    "For images, the definition of what is a feature is less clear-cut, as features of images may correspond to individual pixels, to information automatically extracted by the models to achieve some predictions, or even be the classification targets in other cases.",
    "For example, a model that classifies images of dogs and cats may internally extract features that represent the shape of the ears to make a decision."
  ]
}